A driver was on Saturday injured after footbridge under construction near Nyayo Stadium Roundabout collapses on three cranes forcing closure Langata Rd. Police have diverted vehicles using the route and asked other motorists to avoid it for now. The footbridge was being raised when it collapsed on the cranes on site. Traffic flow affected on adjacent roads as experts clear scene. Nairobi traffic boss Joshua Omukata said they are working hard to clear the scene